<synopsis><code mime="text/x-python">
@accepts(GObject.Value, gint, gfloat)
@returns(none)
def value_set_shader_matrix(value, size, matrix)
</code></synopsis>
<p>Sets @matrix as the contents of @value. The passed <link xref="GValue">GValue</link>
must have been initialized using %CLUTTER_TYPE_SHADER_MATRIX.</p>

